<i>verb</i>: 반추하다 [반ː추하다], 되새김질하다 [되새김질하다/뒈새김질하다], 되새기다 [되새기다/뒈새기다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>반추하다 [반ː추하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. ruminate; reflect</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 여러 번 계속하여 생각하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To constantly think about a matter.</dd><br>
<dd>2. ruminate</dd><br>
<dd>소, 염소 등이 삼킨 먹이를 다시 게워 씹다.</dd><br>
<dd>For cows, goats, etc., to bring food back into their mouths from their stomachs and chew it again.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>되새김질하다 [되새김질하다/뒈새김질하다]</dt><br>
<dd>ruminate; chew the cud</dd><br>
<dd>소나 염소 등의 동물이 한번 삼킨 먹이를 다시 입 안에 내어서 씹다.</dd><br>
<dd>For animals such as cows or goats to bring up food that has been swallowed and chew it again.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>되새기다 [되새기다/뒈새기다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. chew over and over again</dd><br>
<dd>배가 부르거나 입맛이 없거나 해서 음식을 넘기지 않고 입안에서 자꾸 씹다.</dd><br>
<dd>To chew food over and over without swallowing it because one has a full stomach or poor appetite.</dd><br>
<dd>2. ruminate; chew the cud</dd><br>
<dd>소나 염소 등의 동물이 한 번 삼킨 먹이를 다시 입 안에 내어서 씹다.</dd><br>
<dd>For animals such as cows or goats to bring up food that has been swallowed and chew it again.</dd><br>
<dd>3. ruminate; meditate</dd><br>
<dd>지난 일을 다시 떠올려 곰곰이 생각하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To recall something past to one's mind and think it over.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>